52.4	Darrell_Issa	Darrell Issa	Darrell Edward Issa is the U.S. Representative for California's 49th congressional district, serving since 2001. He is a member of the Republican Party. He was formerly a CEO of Directed Electronics, the Vista, California-based manufacturer of automobile security and convenience products. His district consists of portions of southern Riverside County and northern San Diego County. The district was numbered as the 48th District during his first term and was renumbered the 49th after the 2000 Census. Since January 2011, he has served as Chairman of the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/42/Congressman_Darrell_Issa.jpg/220px-Congressman_Darrell_Issa.jpg
